---
title: Cheat's Homemade Veggie Samosa Rolls with Baby Plum Tomato Salad
description: Learn something new in the kitchen by making our Cheat's Homemade Veggie Samosa Rolls. Inspired by the popular south Asian pastries found in India and the Middle East, we make it easier with filo pastry.
